Titolo: Haunted Castle (video game)

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Haunted Castle is a side-scrolling platform game released by Konami for the arcades in 1987. It is the second arcade game in the Castlevania franchise, following Vs. Castlevania, an arcade port of the original 1986 NES video game released exclusively in North America. Unlike the previous arcade title in the franchise, Haunted Castle is not a port,  but a newly-developed game running on custom JAMMA-based hardware.
The game has the player controlling Simon Belmont, who embarks on a journey to save his wife Selena from the clutches of Dracula.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
